          "text": "",
          "color": "#f7f3f3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Part of these distributional differences may be related to dialect, as lambdacism is not uniformly present throughout the Island (Piero's findings) ",
          "color": "#f7f3f3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "",
          "color": "#f7f3f3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "There is other research that suggests this feature may be thematically conditioned",
          "color": "#f7f3f3"
        }
